headline: Moody's Corporation - A Financial Exchange Giant At A Significant Premium
summary: Moody's remains a global leader in credit ratings and analytics, but its current valuation above 36x P/E is historically elevated. See why I rate the MCO stock a Hold.

headline: 2 Large-Cap Stocks Worth Your Attention and 1 We Turn Down
summary: Large-cap stocks usually command their industries because they have the scale to drive market trends. The flip side though is that their sheer size can limit growth as expanding further becomes an increasingly challenging task.
